# Full leaf base, glow flower blooms at corners of mid layer, cross leaf midsection.

# --- BASE (sy=0, full 3x3) ---
S 0 0 0  0 0 0  Leaf
S 0 0 0  1 0 0  Leaf
S 0 0 0  2 0 0  Leaf
S 0 0 0  0 0 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  1 0 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  2 0 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  0 0 2  Leaf
S 0 0 0  1 0 2  Leaf
S 0 0 0  2 0 2  Leaf

# --- MID (sy=1): cross leaf + corner glow flowers ---
S 0 0 0  0 1 0  glow
S 0 0 0  1 1 0  Leaf
S 0 0 0  2 1 0  glow
S 0 0 0  0 1 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  1 1 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  2 1 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  0 1 2  glow
S 0 0 0  1 1 2  Leaf
S 0 0 0  2 1 2  glow
